  "openingNotes": "Welcome the candidate, introduce yourself and FinanceFlow briefly. Outline the interview structure, reiterating the 60% hands-on engineering and 40% technical leadership split. Explain that the goal is to understand their technical depth, leadership style, and how their experience aligns with the Tech Lead role, particularly focusing on our core product for financial operations teams.",
