ncident. \n    *   **Blameless Post-mortems:** After every significant incident, conduct a blameless post-mortem to identify root causes, improve systems, and update runbooks/alerts. We'd focus on systemic improvements rather than individual blame, tracking action items to completion. Regular incident drills would also be beneficial to practice our response."
